Subprog AS_WDOMEXM(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(43563,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
## Action STD
Call AS_WDOMEXM(VALEUR) From SUBEML2
If mkstat=2
 [M]WDOMEXM(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo WDOMEXM(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_WDOMEXM(zc) From W1HRMAT9
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_WDOMEXM(zc) From W1HRMAT9
Gosub _AFF
End

